<br>
For the &quot;evil&quot; research (notes):<br>
The text seems to indicate that to create spells you have to gather several notes and COMBINE THEM in the sages box (maybe in your old research book?). Has anyone tried combining single or several notes??<br>
<br>
For the &quot;neutral&quot; research (runes):<br>
I wonder if old world runes work for this, but as a start I would suggest getting ONLY the mage words and all wizard runes you can come by. Then try combining one rune with each of the equal spell level words. The key seems to be here to limit the words and runes so you dont miss any combinations in the huge number of possible combinations.<br>
<br>
For the &quot;good&quot; research (items):<br>
I would assume that this is the easiest way to get new spells. Just combine an item with an effect in the box. Probably will take some time until such items start appearing in the next rank of planes (perhaps they do not drop in the first set).<br>
<br>
Hoping for some solutions <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
