<br>
First let's look at some of the new tinkering items:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>1. Anizok's Gauze Press - Varified and Triv &gt; 250:<br>
(MAGIC, AMMO, Recommended level of 30. Effect: Summon Bandages (Must Equip. Casting Time: 10.) Wt:5.0, Size: Medium, ALL/ALL)<br>
<br>
Components needed<br>
base prototype, gnomish bolts, static orb, class 6 mana battery, bandage<br>
<br>
1. Necrotic Divining Device - Varified, Triv &gt; 191:<br>
(MAGIC, AMMO, Effect: Track Corpse (Must Equip. Casting Time: 3.0), Wt:0.1, Size: Tiny, ALL/ALL)<br>
<br>
Components needed<br>
base prototype, gnomish bolts, static orb, class 6 mana battery, tiny jain inlaid coffin<br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
In order to make these items, it requires new items to be combined with an old world item.  In this case, the bandage and the tiny jaid inlaid coffin are the focus, and the other items upgrade it in a way.<br>
<br>
This could also be the same with our spells.  <br>
<br>
Combining the notes, items from not turn in, etc. with say, a sword of runes spell.  Could that possible give us one of our summon pet weapons spell?<br>
<br>
Could another combo with our Voc or G. Voc pet spell give us our new pets?<br>
<br>
I'll try these sometime this week, when I gather some items to finish the first part of the quest.  If someone does have the first part finished, maybe you could try these combines? <p><p align="center"><b><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=188590>
